@startuml Candidate_CV

title Candidate - CV Management (Module C)

actor Candidate as "👤 Ứng Viên"

rectangle "CV MANAGEMENT" {
    usecase "Create New\nCV" as C1
    usecase "List My\nCVs" as C2
    usecase "View CV\nDetails" as C3
    usecase "Update CV\nInformation" as C4
    usecase "Delete CV" as C5
    usecase "Set Default\nCV" as C6
    usecase "Upload CV\nPDF File" as C7
}

Candidate --> C1: 1. Create CV
Candidate --> C2: 2. View CVs
C2 --> C3: View details
C3 --> C4: 3. Update info
C3 --> C7: 4. Upload PDF
Candidate --> C5: 5. Delete CV
Candidate --> C6: 6. Set as default

note right of C1
  **Priority:** P0 (Critical)
  **Status:** Need Validation
end note

@enduml
